Love a soft person. The kind of person who kisses your soul instead of your heart.
Life is a mess — yes, but my god, is it ever a beautiful one.
The kind of love that makes you want to be a better person, the kind of love that inspires you, and it will come. It will come.
It’s okay to feel. It’s okay to shut the bathroom door and bawl in front of your mirror about the little things, things that other people have no idea that you’re even upset about.
You might have woken up in bed alone this morning, but I want you to know that someone in this world loves you.
You have dug your soul  out of the dark,  you have fought  to be here;  do not go back  to what buried you.
Stay single until you meet the girl whose love heals you, changes you and makes you better.
